At the club where the bright lights all glow,  
Disco fever begins to take show.  
With a flick and a spin,  
Let the funky begin—  
Platform shoes tap a glittered tableau.  

Mirror balls twirl with shimmering might,  
Polyester suits shining so bright.  
To the beat of the jam,  
Crowds go bam, bam, kablam!  
